name: Chihuahua In Space
description: The projects includes a game, NFTs, staking and their governance token $CIS which is 2% tax. The tokens supply is 500,000,000,000 and their staking dApp offers 31,445,000% APY, while allowing them to 5mil $CIS tokens per wallet for 60 days. Their P2E includes collecting Baby Chihuahuas and earning rewards for saving each of them. Players also fuel their rocket with $CIS to fly and go on quests. Game already Available on Anroid and soon coming to the iOS.
